45:45.650 --> 45:48.200
Oh, no, my plans for
a quiet evening at home

45:48.250 --> 45:49.500
kind of fell through, so...

45:49.550 --> 45:52.740
Then it's fate. I'll take it.

45:52.790 --> 45:54.110
Hey.

45:54.160 --> 45:57.980
- It's a good turnout, right?
- PJ was loved.

45:58.030 --> 46:00.040
So what are you reading?

46:00.090 --> 46:03.210
You know, it would be
everything if you read.

46:03.260 --> 46:06.220
Yeah, I, uh, haven't decided.

46:06.270 --> 46:08.450
Don't worry about it.

46:08.500 --> 46:11.260
- We are just glad you're here.
- Thank you.

46:11.310 --> 46:14.090
- Hey, Jocelyn.
- Hi.

46:19.150 --> 46:22.630
This is KD. Leave
a message and have a blessed day.

46:25.450 --> 46:27.210
