what you're talking about!

47:57.910 --> 48:00.230
- I don't have no cocaine!
- Shut up!

48:04.250 --> 48:06.910
Holy shit, Officer, that is not mine!

48:06.960 --> 48:08.110
- Shut up!
- Right. On the fence.

48:08.160 --> 48:09.210
Don't move!

48:09.260 --> 48:10.210
I'm not a fucking drug dealer!

48:10.260 --> 48:11.510
Yeah, right.

48:11.560 --> 48:12.910
I swear to God, man, I'm not lying, man!

48:12.960 --> 48:14.650
- Shut up!
- Please! It's not mine!

48:14.700 --> 48:18.350
What's up, 2Pac?

48:18.400 --> 48:20.820
I need you to listen to me.

48:20.870 --> 48:23.660
This has been a test of
the Emergency Bobo System.

48:23.710 --> 48:25.260
