permanently fucked up!

48:30.680 --> 48:32.400
What? What?

48:32.450 --> 48:33.800
- Don't move.
- Man...

48:33.850 --> 48:35.970
Khalil, Khalil, Khalil, you made a mistake.

48:36.020 --> 48:37.540
You stepped into the ring without knowing

48:37.590 --> 48:38.940
