however, that I will be merciful

48:58.010 --> 49:01.030
and drop all the charges against
you if you agree to my terms.

49:01.080 --> 49:03.160
Yeah! Absolutely, what
are... what are the terms?

49:03.210 --> 49:06.300
Please, please shut up, dummy.
I'm getting to the terms.

49:06.350 --> 49:09.370
First, you bring me the marriage
certificate, the original.

49:09.420 --> 49:12.100
Second, you never, and I
mean never the fuck ever,

49:12.150 --> 49:16.170
