49:18.760 --> 49:20.980
Yeah, yeah, absolutely, yeah!

49:21.030 --> 49:23.820
Good, then this concludes our test

49:23.870 --> 49:25.920
of the Emergency Bobo System.

49:25.970 --> 49:28.990
You may now resume back to your
regularly scheduled program.

49:29.040 --> 49:30.620
